1. System Overview
The FNF Agent Stack is a Python-based AI content pipeline that automates research, content planning, and WordPress publishing for the Funny not Funny advocacy website. It runs on your local Windows 11 machine and connects to external services via API.

1.1 Architecture
Three agents work in sequence to form a complete content production pipeline:

Agent
File
Purpose
Output
Agent 1
agent_1_research.py
Web research
.md brief in output/
Agent 2
agent_2_content.py
Calendar planning
Google Sheet update
Agent 3
agent_3_wordpress.py
WordPress publishing
Draft/live WP post


